0-7fffffffffff: @rootpgt
800000000000-ffff7fffffffffff: NONE
ffff800000000000-ffffffffffffffff: @rootpgt

KV -> PHYS:
0-7fffffffffff: @rootpgt
800000000000-ffff7fffffffffff: NONE
ffff800000000000-ffffffffffffffff: @rootpgt

KPHYS -> DIRECT:

MACHPHYS -> KPHYS:
0-ffffffffffffff: @machphys_kphys
100000000000000-ffffffffffffffff: NONE

KPHYS -> MACHPHYS:
0-ffffffffffffff: @kphys_machphys
100000000000000-ffffffffffffffff: NONE
